{"image_id": "SYK_2017_page_10", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "STRYKER CORPORATION                                                                                                                         2017 FORM 10-K", "bbox": [75.0, 22.3, 1199.5, 45.6]}, {"text": "Dollar amounts in millions except per share amounts or as otherwise specified.", "bbox": [79.2, 1557.6, 628.7, 1573.9]}, {"text": "8", "bbox": [1183.5, 1557.6, 1191.7, 1573.9]}, {"text": "ITEM 7.", "bbox": [81.2, 77.9, 146.9, 98.9]}, {"text": "MANAGEMENT’S DISCUSSION AND ANALYSIS OF FINANCIAL CONDITION AND RESULTS OF OPERATIONS.", "bbox": [208.3, 77.9, 1175.4, 98.9]}, {"text": "Overview of 2017", "bbox": [75.0, 115.9, 228.2, 136.9]}, {"text": "Our goal is to achieve sales growth at the high-end of the medical", "bbox": [75.0, 144.7, 624.0, 165.6]}, {"text": "technology (MedTech) industry and maintain our capital allocation", "bbox": [75.0, 167.1, 623.9, 188.0]}, {"text": "strategy that prioritizes: (1) Acquisitions, (2) Dividends and (3)", "bbox": [75.0, 189.7, 624.0, 210.6]}, {"text": "Share repurchases.", "bbox": [75.0, 212.1, 238.6, 233.0]}, {"text": "In 2017 we achieved reported net sales growth of 9.9%. Excluding", "bbox": [75.0, 240.9, 624.0, 261.9]}, {"text": "the impact of acquisitions, net sales grew 7.1% in constant currency,", "bbox": [75.0, 263.4, 624.0, 284.4]}, {"text": "in line with our ongoing goal to grow organic sales at the high-end", "bbox": [75.0, 285.9, 624.0, 306.9]}, {"text": "of MedTech. We reported net earnings of $1,020 and net earnings", "bbox": [75.0, 308.4, 624.0, 329.4]}, {"text": "per diluted share of $2.68. Excluding the impact of certain items,", "bbox": [75.0, 327.9, 623.9, 351.9]}, {"text": "we achieved adjusted net earnings of $2,465 and growth of 11.9%", "bbox": [75.0, 353.4, 624.0, 374.4]}, {"text": "in adjusted net earnings per diluted share(1).", "bbox": [75.0, 372.9, 444.3, 396.9]}, {"text": "We continued our capital allocation strategy by investing $831 in", "bbox": [75.0, 404.7, 624.0, 425.6]}, {"text": "acquisitions, paying $636 in dividends to our shareholders and", "bbox": [75.0, 427.2, 623.9, 448.1]}, {"text": "using $230 for share repurchases.", "bbox": [75.0, 449.7, 359.5, 470.6]}, {"text": "In December 2017 we announced a definitive merger agreement", "bbox": [75.0, 478.4, 624.0, 499.4]}, {"text": "to acquire Entellus Medical, Inc. (Entellus), a high-growth global", "bbox": [75.0, 500.9, 623.9, 521.9]}, {"text": "medical technology company focused on delivering superior patient", "bbox": [75.0, 523.4, 624.0, 544.4]}, {"text": "and physician experiences through products designed for the", "bbox": [75.0, 545.9, 624.0, 566.9]}, {"text": "minimally invasive treatment of various ear, nose and throat (ENT)", "bbox": [75.0, 568.4, 624.0, 589.4]}, {"text": "disease states, for $24.00 per share, or total consideration of", "bbox": [75.0, 590.9, 624.0, 611.9]}, {"text": "approximately $662. We expect the acquisition to close in February", "bbox": [75.0, 613.4, 624.0, 634.4]}, {"text": "2018.", "bbox": [75.0, 635.9, 127.1, 656.9]}, {"text": "In September 2017 we acquired NOVADAQ Technologies Inc.", "bbox": [75.0, 664.7, 624.0, 685.6]}, {"text": "(NOVADAQ) for total consideration of approximately $716.", "bbox": [75.0, 687.2, 624.0, 708.1]}, {"text": "NOVADAQ is a leading developer of fluorescence imaging", "bbox": [75.0, 709.7, 623.9, 730.6]}, {"text": "technology that provides surgeons with visualization of blood flow", "bbox": [656.2, 115.9, 1205.2, 136.9]}, {"text": "in vessels and related tissue perfusion in cardiac, cardiovascular,", "bbox": [656.2, 138.4, 1205.2, 159.4]}, {"text": "gastrointestinal,", "bbox": [656.2, 160.8, 792.8, 181.8]}, {"text": "plastic,", "bbox": [811.5, 160.8, 875.0, 181.8]}, {"text": "microsurgical", "bbox": [893.8, 160.8, 1009.4, 181.8]}, {"text": "and", "bbox": [1028.1, 160.8, 1064.6, 181.8]}, {"text": "reconstructive", "bbox": [1083.3, 160.8, 1205.2, 181.8]}, {"text": "procedures. Refer to Note 5 to our Consolidated Financial", "bbox": [656.2, 183.4, 1205.2, 204.4]}, {"text": "Statements for further information.", "bbox": [656.2, 205.8, 940.7, 226.8]}, {"text": "In August 2017 we initiated a voluntary product recall involving", "bbox": [656.2, 234.7, 1205.2, 255.6]}, {"text": "specific lots of our Sage Products (Sage) Oral Care products. We", "bbox": [656.2, 257.2, 1205.2, 278.1]}, {"text": "took this action in response to a Warning Letter received from the", "bbox": [656.2, 279.7, 1205.2, 300.6]}, {"text": "United States Food and Drug Administration (FDA) dated July 17,", "bbox": [656.2, 302.2, 1205.2, 323.1]}, {"text": "2017, which set forth concerns regarding the potential for cross-", "bbox": [656.2, 324.7, 1200.0, 345.6]}, {"text": "contamination of Oral Care solutions manufactured by a third-party", "bbox": [656.2, 347.2, 1205.2, 368.1]}, {"text": "supplier on equipment also used to manufacture non-", "bbox": [656.2, 369.7, 1200.0, 390.6]}, {"text": "pharmaceutical products.  We discontinued business with the third-", "bbox": [656.2, 392.2, 1200.0, 413.1]}, {"text": "party supplier and the Oral Care solutions are now being", "bbox": [656.2, 414.7, 1205.2, 435.6]}, {"text": "manufactured in-house. We resumed shipping Oral Care products", "bbox": [656.2, 437.2, 1205.2, 458.1]}, {"text": "in October and returned to full supply capacity by the end of 2017.", "bbox": [656.2, 459.7, 1200.0, 480.6]}, {"text": "We also placed Sage cloth-based products on a temporary ship", "bbox": [656.2, 488.4, 1205.2, 509.4]}, {"text": "hold during the third quarter in response to concerns set forth in the", "bbox": [656.2, 510.9, 1205.2, 531.9]}, {"text": "FDA Warning Letter regarding testing methods used for all Sage", "bbox": [656.2, 533.4, 1205.2, 554.4]}, {"text": "products containing solutions. We resumed shipping products", "bbox": [656.2, 555.9, 1205.2, 576.9]}, {"text": "manufactured in-house and tested under the testing method", "bbox": [656.2, 578.4, 1205.2, 599.4]}, {"text": "required by FDA in September 2017 and returned to full supply", "bbox": [656.2, 600.9, 1205.2, 621.9]}, {"text": "capacity by the end of 2017.", "bbox": [656.2, 623.4, 901.2, 644.4]}, {"text": "In January 2017 we issued $500 of senior unsecured notes. Refer", "bbox": [656.2, 652.2, 1205.2, 673.1]}, {"text": "to Note 9 to our Consolidated Financial Statements for further", "bbox": [656.2, 674.7, 1205.2, 695.6]}, {"text": "information.", "bbox": [656.2, 697.2, 759.4, 718.1]}, {"text": "(1) Refer to \"Non-GAAP Financial Measures\" for a discussion of non-GAAP financial measures used in this report and a reconciliation to the most directly", "bbox": [75.0, 735.2, 1204.6, 756.5]}, {"text": "comparable GAAP financial measure.", "bbox": [75.0, 757.8, 352.6, 776.5]}, {"text": "CONSOLIDATED RESULTS OF OPERATIONS", "bbox": [75.0, 820.1, 474.0, 841.1]}, {"text": "Percent Net Sales", "bbox": [813.3, 861.6, 936.5, 877.9]}, {"text": "Percentage Change", "bbox": [1036.0, 861.6, 1172.2, 877.9]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [506.7, 882.4, 539.1, 898.7]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [594.2, 882.4, 626.6, 898.7]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [681.7, 882.4, 714.1, 898.7]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [777.5, 882.4, 809.9, 898.7]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [865.0, 882.4, 897.4, 898.7]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [946.3, 882.4, 978.7, 898.7]}, {"text": "2017/2016", "bbox": [1021.8, 882.4, 1090.7, 898.7]}, {"text": "2016/2015", "bbox": [1117.6, 882.4, 1186.5, 898.7]}, {"text": "Net sales", "bbox": [81.2, 903.3, 145.3, 919.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [485.4, 903.3, 493.5, 919.6]}, {"text": "12,444 $", "bbox": [517.1, 903.3, 581.0, 919.6]}, {"text": "11,325 $", "bbox": [604.6, 903.3, 668.5, 919.6]}, {"text": "9,946", "bbox": [700.1, 903.3, 736.6, 919.6]}, {"text": "100.0%", "bbox": [787.9, 903.3, 837.4, 919.6]}, {"text": "100.0%", "bbox": [875.4, 903.3, 924.9, 919.6]}, {"text": "100.0%", "bbox": [950.4, 903.3, 999.9, 919.6]}, {"text": "9.9 %", "bbox": [1065.9, 903.3, 110